Detailed records of the actual work that was performed on the perimeter.

1) Reports of any injuries, accidents or collisions involving a scooter or bike;
2) Work orders, maintenance records, maintenance activity sheets, or plans;
3) Complaints, reports, accidents or incidents regarding uneven pavement;
4) Complaints, reports, accidents or incidents concerning manhole covers not being even or flush
with the pavement
